author: Barco van Rhijn
category: Networking    
---

I've been meaning to run a Radius server for some time now. I toyed with this back in 2019 but then ran out of time.

So I'm back and my initial need is to get something up that will help with better Wifi Authentication. 
A new lockdown reality is that Wifi is something people want to steal actively for fun. 

I've hardened out the local gear and am now looking for an additional layer of protection.

Meet FreeRadius. A simple idea with many moving parts to accomplish simply put Authentication, Authorization and Accounting. 

That's the just of it. And 